      "text": "0. Llega el webhook POST desde BookStack y en base al tipo\nevento se ejecuta el flujo correspondiente:\n\n\n\nEvento: \"page.create\"\n\n\n1. POST `/webhook/bookstack` `{ event: \"page.create\",\npage_id: 42 }`\n2. Postgres: ¿existe `page_id 42`? → No\n3. GET `docs.frba/api/pages/42` → markdown\n4. Docling: limpiar markdown\n5. ChunkingService: dividir en chunks\n6. EmbeddingService: generar vectores\n7. Qdrant: upsert chunks (collection `tech_manuals`)\n8. Postgres: INSERT `pages` (`page_id`, `hash`,\n`version=1`, ...)\n9. HTTP 200 OK\n\n\nEvento: \"page.update\"\n\n\n1. POST `/webhook/bookstack` `{ event: \"page.update\",\npage_id: 42 }`\n2. GET `docs.frba/api/pages/42` → markdown\n3. MD5(markdown) → hash nuevo\n4. Postgres: SELECT WHERE `page_id=42` → hash viejo\n\n   * hash igual → nada cambió → HTTP 200, fin\n   * hash distinto → continuar\n5. Docling: limpiar markdown\n6. ChunkingService: dividir en chunks\n7. EmbeddingService: generar vectores\n8. Qdrant: DELETE chunks WHERE `page_id=42`\n9. Qdrant: upsert chunks nuevos\n10. Postgres: UPDATE `pages` SET `hash`, `version+1`,\n`ingested_at`\n11. HTTP 200 OK\n\n\n\nEvento: \"page.delete\"\n\n\n1. POST `/webhook/bookstack` `{ event: \"page.delete\",\npage_id: 42 }`\n2. Qdrant: DELETE chunks WHERE `page_id=42`\n3. Postgres: DELETE WHERE `page_id=42`\n4. HTTP 200 OK",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "0. Llega el webhook POST desde BookStack y en base al tipo evento se ejecuta el flujo correspondiente:\n\n\n\nEvento: \"page.create\"\n\n\n1. POST `/webhook/bookstack` `{ event: \"page.create\", page_id: 42 }`\n2. Postgres: ¿existe `page_id 42`? → No\n3. GET `docs.frba/api/pages/42` → markdown\n4. Docling: limpiar markdown\n5. ChunkingService: dividir en chunks\n6. EmbeddingService: generar vectores\n7. Qdrant: upsert chunks (collection `tech_manuals`)\n8. Postgres: INSERT `pages` (`page_id`, `hash`, `version=1`, ...)\n9. HTTP 200 OK\n\n\nEvento: \"page.update\"\n\n\n1. POST `/webhook/bookstack` `{ event: \"page.update\", page_id: 42 }`\n2. GET `docs.frba/api/pages/42` → markdown\n3. MD5(markdown) → hash nuevo\n4. Postgres: SELECT WHERE `page_id=42` → hash viejo\n\n   * hash igual → nada cambió → HTTP 200, fin\n   * hash distinto → continuar\n5. Docling: limpiar markdown\n6. ChunkingService: dividir en chunks\n7. EmbeddingService: generar vectores\n8. Qdrant: DELETE chunks WHERE `page_id=42`\n9. Qdrant: upsert chunks nuevos\n10. Postgres: UPDATE `pages` SET `hash`, `version+1`, `ingested_at`\n11. HTTP 200 OK\n\n\n\nEvento: \"page.delete\"\n\n\n1. POST `/webhook/bookstack` `{ event: \"page.delete\", page_id: 42 }`\n2. Qdrant: DELETE chunks WHERE `page_id=42`\n3. Postgres: DELETE WHERE `page_id=42`\n4. HTTP 200 OK",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
